Question : 
How to make a component containing other components ? 

Answer : 
1. base your component on some kind of TWinCotnrol, like a panel 
2. override the constructor and create your internal objects there. 
3. set the parent properties of your internal objects to the owner object (your 
new component) 
4. override the destroy method and free your components. 
  
  
  
  
